      "updated": 1776083691460,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Pac man to Ghost collision detection\n1- get the canvas rectangle of Pac Man\n2- get the canvas rectangle of the Ghost\n3- check if there is any intersection between the 2 rectangles.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
