      "text": "Pac man to Suger and super suger collision detection\n1- get the canvas rectangle of pac man.\n2- get the canvas rectangle of the sugar or the super sugar.\n3- check if there is any intersection between the 2 rectangles.\n\n** which sugar should be considered ?\n",
